title: Valley of the Kings [1954 - USA] Robert Taylor adventure
description:
Valley of the Kings (1954 - USA)

Adventure

starring . . . . Robert Taylor, Eleanor Parker, Carlos Thompson
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0047641/


Archaeologists seek tombs and treasures of ancient Egypt, struggling with grave-robbers, smugglers and desert tribes. It was possible to film on location in Egypt as it was before the pro-Soviet Colonel Gamal Abdel Nasser seized power. After 1954 few Western films were made in Egypt due to the country's increasing ties with the Soviet Union and China.
